<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>时间 on 素履独行</title><link>/tags/%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/</link><description>Recent content in 时间 on 素履独行</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 May 2021 14:00:41 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/tags/%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>假如时间有温度</title><link>/posts/%E5%81%87%E5%A6%82%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%A9%E5%BA%A6/</link><pubDate>Mon, 03 May 2021 14:00:41 +0000</pubDate><guid>/posts/%E5%81%87%E5%A6%82%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%A9%E5%BA%A6/</guid><description>我一直在想，世事无常，该是一种什么样的感觉。直到我读到夏目先生的《我是猫》，先生在书中不无感慨地写道，“世事变迁就像猫的眼珠一样变幻莫测”。</description></item><item><title>一个由服务器时区引发的 Bug</title><link>/posts/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E6%97%B6%E5%8C%BA%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E7%9A%84-bug/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 Jun 2018 11:03:57 +0000</pubDate><guid>/posts/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E6%97%B6%E5%8C%BA%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E7%9A%84-bug/</guid><description>太阳照常升起，在每个需要挤公交车上班的日子里，即使窗外早已大雨如注。想来只有在周末，太阳会陪着我一起起床，所谓睡觉睡到自然醒，在雨天里保持晴</description></item><item><title>行走在消逝中</title><link>/posts/%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B0%E5%9C%A8%E6%B6%88%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%AD/</link><pubDate>Thu, 15 Mar 2018 21:29:47 +0000</pubDate><guid>/posts/%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B0%E5%9C%A8%E6%B6%88%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%AD/</guid><description>{% meting &amp;ldquo;523845740&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;netease&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;song&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;autoplay&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;mutex:false&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;listmaxheight:340px&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;preload:none&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;theme:#ad7a86&amp;rdquo;%} 从昨天到今天，关于霍金逝世的消息，一直在朋友圈里刷屏。昨天同事告诉我这个消息的时候，我心底先是一片恍惚，而后习惯性地打开</description></item></channel></rss>